Automated bug and vulnerability audits of Linux distributions

A number of vulnerabilites were discovered using these audits. Additionally many non
security related bug reports resulted from this work.

Memset(x,y,0) Bugs
------------------

Debian are now incorporating automated checks for this class of bug inspired by this
audit [1].

[1] http://lists.debian.org/debian-devel/2011/01/msg00656.html
    https://github.com/danmar/cppcheck/commit/6ec4497919363ca3a81b61ce8121a9b48e46fe63

